...in case you're wondering

Can I join you?

We welcome anyone who would like to join us for any length of the route . Please note that this ride is entirely unsupported and, although we have a route planned, subject to daily changes based on weather, road closures, and other random acts of adventure.


Can I help you raise money?

You can absolutely. Please get in touch and let us know how you'd like to help.


Where is the money going?

Weâ€™re donating 100% of the funds raised to NAMI as a DIY project. You can read a detailed breakdown of how NAMI uses the money we donate on their website (link forthcoming).


Is my donation tax deductable?

If you donate via this website or our NAMI page, your donation is 100% tax deductable. Purchases of goods, cash/venmo donations, etc. are generally not deductable unless you reach out to us.


What will NAMI do with the money you raise?

You can read more about the services offered by NAMI here (link).
